#: APP-MANAGER:248
msgid ""
"Before proceeding with any task, where do you want to install apps?\n"
"\n"
"SYNTAX: /FULLPATH/TO/DIRNAME\n"
"EXAMPLE: $HOME/My-apps\n"
"\n"
"NOTE: Any spaces in the path will be replaced for dashes\n"
"NOTE: If no input is given then \\\"~/Applications\\\" will be used as "
"default\n"
"\n"
"if you wish to later change the location, first remove all the programs and "
"then edit the \\\"$APPMANCONFIG/appman-config\\\" file."
msgstr ""
"Pre nastavljanja sa bilo kojim poslom, gde bi želeo da instaliraš "
"aplikacije?\n"
"\n"
"SINTAKSA: /CELA-PUTANJA/KA/IMENU-DIREKTORIJUMA\n"
"PRIMER: $HOME/Moje-aplikacije\n"
"\n"
"NAPOMENA: Svaki razmak u putanji će biti zamenjen crtom\n"
"NAPOMENA: Ako ništa nije dato onda će \\\"~/Applications\\\" fabrički da se "
"koristi\n"
"\n"
"ako želiš kasnije da promeniš lokaciju, prvo obriši sve programe i onda "
"izmeni \\\"$APPMANCONFIG/appman-config\\\" fajl."

